Created an ebs storage on console 30GB
===============================
Then do this below steps -:
----------------------------------

Created a StorageClass with dsc.yaml on dsc dir 
apiVersion: storage.k8s.io/v1
kind: StorageClass
metadata:
  name: aws-ebs
  annotations:
    storageclass.kubernetes.io/is-default-class: "true"
provisioner: kubernetes.io/aws-ebs
parameters:
  type: gp2
  fsType: ext4
reclaimPolicy: Retain
volumeBindingMode: Immediate

Created a PV -:
============
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolume
metadata:
  name: pv
spec:
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteOnce
  awsElasticBlockStore:
    fsType: xfs
    volumeID: vol-0db9ef113925fd943
  capacity:
    storage: 30Gi
  persistentVolumeReclaimPolicy: Retain
  storageClassName: aws-ebs
  volumeMode: Filesystem

Created an pvc -:
=============
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  labels:
    app: elasticsearch-master
  name: elasticsearch-master-elasticsearch-master-0
  namespace: elk
spec:
  accessModes:
    - ReadWriteOnce
  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 30Gi
  storageClassName: aws-ebs
  volumeName: pv
========================================================================

Then Verify the PV                 - kubectl get pv
Verify PVC               - kubectl get pvc 
Verify the storageclass  - kubectl get sc 
